Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:55.84,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:02:02.81,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久 我一直将你的后背
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:06.98,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作我的依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:14.11,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来将自己身处的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:20.74,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作是临时的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:24.29,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避着 逃避着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.20,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃向梦想的世界
